# Summary
This documentation page explains how to add descriptions to events, event properties, and user properties in Amplitude, including steps for adding descriptions through the details panel and uploading event images for higher-tier customers. It also mentions the ability to bulk update event descriptions by downloading, modifying, and re-uploading the schema.

